@akshonclip It's really sad that the cost of living in this country has gotten so high it's forcing people to leave especially if they've served this country. That said I plan to live as an expat within the next year and have been researching locations for the past several years. I'm not leaving solely for cost of living since I'm still making it, but I agree it's gotten nuts. 

If your friends main concern is cost and you are interested, I can give you some ideas of places to look into that would suit them and yet not be a hell scape like Mexico. Like right off the top of my head, tell your friends to look into Paraguay. It's way cheaper than Mexico but safer, cleaner, welcoming of Americans and not run by cartels.

I've been researching other countries for a couple of years. I'm not leaving because I hate the US, I just have a lot of things I want to do with the rest of my life hah

